{"tid":1923822,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人行定向降準 釋放長期資金5500億","createTime":"2020-03-13T09:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T10:14:29.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"863795444a6d6898125eb4960bf248426dd75d51","tid":1923822,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"【人行定向降準 釋放長期資金5500億】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/33dqaW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33dqaW8&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=92b0de4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/33dqaW8</a><br />\n<br />\n為支持實體經濟發展，降低社會融資實際成本，#中國人民銀行 決定於3月16日實施普惠金融定向降準，對達到考核標準的銀行定向降準0.5至1個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n在此之外，對符合條件的股份制商業銀行再額外定向降準1個百分點，支持發放普惠金融領域貸款。以上定向降準共釋放長期資金5500億元人民幣。<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n最新 📣📣《信報》+《信報月刊》訂閱優惠<br />\n了解更多：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/ejfdncom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fejfdncom&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=70b31c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/ejfdncom</a><br />\n <br />\n#信報 #即時新聞 #經濟發展"},{"pid":"473e4eefe782266fc57233a9885b08d29f55b1bd","tid":1923822,"uid":247180,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"一定升到仆街"},{"pid":"2daf7b019c2efa740149cf4b21aebe74473708c0","tid":1923822,"uid":32782,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"先5500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國佬放1.5兆出來 仲要係美金"},{"pid":"e49a1d9a4606480a5962dfb5934b8f18fab9bca2","tid":1923822,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2daf7b019c2efa740149cf4b21aebe74473708c0","tid":1923822,"uid":32782,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"先5500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國佬放1.5兆出來 仲要係美金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"我都覺5500億太少，可能見慣香港D億億聲大